imagine we have a bug on signup form,
we create new branch to working on it in isolated area!
in next lessons we will merge it.


1.git branch bugfix

2.git branch -m bugfix bugfix/signup-form   //renaming this new branch
                                            //to better name

3.git switch bugfix/signup-form             //we can use "checkout" command
                                            //but checkout has some other application (it's move head pointer)
                                            //so it is better to use "switch" to switch branch.

Note: use "git branch" to find current branch
      * bugfix/signup-form
        main

4.imagine we add some line on "branches 1" file,
  to solve the bug!
  we commit this lines on bugfix/signup-form  branch
  (so these lines not accessible on main branch
   our working directory changed through branches)

Note: Mosh use venus folder (we have it in section3),
      but because it is submodule, we can not see inside commit
      from here, so we use "branches 1" file.

----------------------------------------
git log on main branch:
                       66580ec (HEAD -> main) create branch         //we can not see our commit on bugfix/signup-form branch
                       0af669d create branch                        //because it's above us!
                       b970500 branches                             //we have just main pointer
                       39fcaae use UI                               //we have not any access to that above commit!
                       07de7c5 tag                                  //(we can see it by --all here)

git log on bugfix/signup-form:
                              7c4a76d (HEAD ->bugfix/signup-form) fix bug    //we have access to main commit
                              66580ec (main) create branch                   //because our last commit (7c4a76d)
                              0af669d create branch                          //has a pointer to it
                              b970500 branches                               //it's part of our history
                              39fcaae use UI                                 //we create "bugfix/signup-form" branch
                                                                             //on this commit (66580ec)


